  ### [helpers](https://middlemanapp.com/basics/helper_methods/)

  - Link Helpers `link_to`
  - Output Helpers `content_for(:javascript)`
  - Asset Helpers `stylesheet_link_tag`

  <br>
  ```ruby
    = image_tag lorem.image('300x400'), alt: 'seo matter'
  ```
  Produces:
  ```html
    <img src="http://placehold.it/300x400" alt="seo matter">
  ```
