  ##### Bonus:

  Easier to upgrade to a rails app (with [codeless](https://github.com/flexbox/codeless))

  Stylesheets, fonts, images, and JavaScript files go in the `/source/assets/` directory.

  Vendor stylesheets and JavaScripts should go in each of their `/bower_components/` directories.

      codeless/
      ├── bower_components/
      │    └── ...
      ├── source/
      │   ├── assets/
      |   |    ├── stylesheets/application.scss
      |   |    └── javascripts/application.js.coffee
      |   └── ...

